Description: DebMonitor tracks Debian packages across a fleet of hosts
 DebMonitor is a Django-based web application that allows the tracking of Debian
 packages installed across a fleet of hosts, along with their pending
 software/security updates.
 It also provides a standalone command line script (CLI) that, when distributed
 on the target hosts, allows automatic updates of DebMonitor's database
 using APT and DPKG hooks.


Package:python3-debmonitor
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${python3:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: DebMonitor tracks Debian packages across a fleet of hosts (Python modules)
 DebMonitor is a Django-based web application that allows to track Debian
 packages installed across a fleet of hosts, along with their pending
 software/security updates.
 It provides also a standalone command line script (CLI) that, when distributed
 on the target hosts, allows automatic updates of DebMonitor's database
 using APT and DPKG hooks.
